    "en": {
      "title": "35,000 metric tons of gasoline will be landed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kanchana Wijesekara, Minister of Power and Energy, said that the unloading of petrol from a ship carrying 35,000 metric tons of octane 92 petrol started last night (30).",
        "The Minister further said that the congestion of the last few days regarding fuel distribution has been ended and 4000 metric tons of diesel and 3000 metric tons of petrol will be released per day."
      ],
